{"tid":2210694,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"台灣應該趁機發起全面去中化運動，咁先能夠保障民主自由！","createTime":"2020-09-20T15:00:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T06:26:28.000Z","uid":245856,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"815c73e45a584425ed33b70fc3b6e391a7bbf074","tid":2210694,"uid":245856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T15:00:58.000Z","msg":"依家全球都圍中，喺呢個形勢底下台灣又要受到大陸嘅軍事威脅。如果要保障台灣嘅民主自由，呢個時候就一定要台灣需要一場全面去中化運動。大膽作個預想<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 廢除年號、放棄大陸主權、更改國號及旗號<br />\n<br />\n2. 銷毁國內所有關於「中華民國」的物件，例如兩蔣銅像、孫文銅像、中華民國國旗、中華民國宣傳品等等。<br />\n<br />\n3. 將中國國民黨定性為國奸，清算其黨產，並立法禁止以「中國國民黨」牌頭在國內活動。 以防止國民黨在國內組織任何勢力動搖到國家穩定。<br />\n<br />\n4. 將孫中山定性為賣國分子，立法禁止掛孫中山畫像。<br />\n<br />\n5. 禁止提倡「中華民國」及與「中華民國」有關既言論、文字、圖像、旗號。表達方式包括任何明示或暗示。<br />\n<br />\n凡觸犯第二、三、四條者一律當賣國投共處理，判處適當刑罰。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 刑罰包括凍結其、其直屬家人、其親友甚至其朋友資產，亦可派人對犯人作二十四小時人身監控，以防止犯人與賣國者連繫。 嚴重者判處監禁刑期，甚至死刑。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n淨係F F呀都流晒口水，咁既話台灣就真係越嚟越強大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5069b511026339e9c5c2c35ed7daadc0c1632fac","tid":2210694,"uid":197005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T15:07:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d2629d4a1d74b197d27748f2c05ad40d21ad084","tid":2210694,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T15:28:51.000Z","msg":"去國民黨化唔係去民主化ok?"},{"pid":"36e53f8ec52c18b3ba7183eb32c3847162f4e538","tid":2210694,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T15:37:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16aa78fe59abc4c3ea3d79d1223a4ded902e935d","tid":2210694,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T06:26:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}